{
  "title": "customer summary",
  "description": "This space provides a summary view of sales performance by product category, enabling analysis of sales volume, revenue, and pricing trends.\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- Analyze total orders, total revenue, total units sold, and average unit price by product category\n- Compare sales performance across different product categories\n- Identify categories with the highest sales or revenue contribution\n- Assess average pricing trends across categories\n\n**Limitations:**\n- Does not provide data at the individual product or customer level\n- Cannot analyze sales performance over time (no date or time fields)\n- Lacks geographic, channel, or promotional breakdowns",
